result.notes: On 1 September the Foreign and Commonwealth Office (FCO) merged with the Department for International Development (DFID) to form Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office.  These data gives details of the workforce management information data for the Foreign and Commonwealth Office. These figures are not official statistics. They are internal workforce management information published in the interests of transparency.
